      <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 my-10" style="background:var(--primary-lt)">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3" style="color:var(--primary)">Why the QR code makes a difference</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-0">Adding a QR code to an invitation is not just a technical detail — it gives the guest a comfortable way to confirm in the moment they read the invitation, without having to remember to do it later. That translates directly into more confirmations and less manual follow-up.</p>
